(=== BOOK SUMMARY ===) Tj T*
(This book is a foundational academic reference for modeling serial and parallel robot) Tj T*
(manipulators. It provides highly detailed methods for deriving geometric, kinematic,) Tj T*
(and dynamic models, with a strong focus on parameter identification, stiffness) Tj T*
(analysis, and closed-loop control of complex robotic architectures.) Tj T*
T*
